*(''insane person''): [[loony]], [[nutbag]], [[nutcase]], [[nutter]]
*(''the head''): [[bonce]], [[noodle]] (See further synonyms under [[head]])
*(''a testicle''): [[ball]], [[bollock]] (''taboo slang''), [[nads]]

